Package mmarquee.automation

Domain classes used to encapsulate the ms ui automation libraries.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AutomationTreeWalker.AutomationElementVisitor
    A visitor as used by AutomationTreeWalker.walk(AutomationElementVisitor, AutomationElement).
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AutomationElement
    Wrapper for the underlying automation element.
    AutomationEventHandler  
    AutomationTreeWalker
    Wrapper for the AutomationTreeWalker.
    BaseAutomation
    Base class to have underlying behaviour.
    CacheRequest
    Encapsulated the cache request.
    Ole32Wrapper
    Wrapper for the access to Ole32, which only exists on Windows, so tests can't be run on Linux, etc.
    UIAutomation
    The base automation wrapper.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ControlType
    Enumeration for the control-type.
    EventID
    Automation Event Identifiers.
    MetaDataID
    Meta Data Identifiers.
    PatternID
    Automation Pattern Identifiers.
    PropertyID
    Automation Property Identifiers.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AutomationException
    An exception thrown when there is an error returned by the underlying automation library.
    ConversionFailure
    Thrown when a conversion to an interface fails.
    ElementNotFoundException
    Thrown when an element is not found.
    ItemNotFoundException
    Thrown when an item is not found.
